<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an die Städebünde zu Schwaben, Franken und am Bodensee, und die anderen Reichsstädte zu Schwaben in der Hegaualb und in Franken</head><p>Der Rat erklärt sich wegen Weinsberg zu einer Gesandtschaft zu Konrad IX. von Weinsberg bereit und bittet um Mitteilung des Termins.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_211" id="104v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_211_r1l13">Des <expan>heılıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Römıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> Reıchs Stette <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> . der <expan>v<ex>er</ex>eynu<ex>n</ex>ge</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l14">Jn Swoben vmb den Bodemſee vnd in franken . vnd auch der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l15"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Stette in Swoben vnder Ek vnd in franken / als ſıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l16">nehſt ʒu vlme bey <expan>eınand<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein . <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_211_r1l17"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>Fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> / als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt / vvıe Jr von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> guten freẅnd ~ der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l18">von <expan>weinſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / meynet eẅr erber <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ʒutun ʒu dem edeln </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l19"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ʒu <expan>vveinſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> ob der in kürcʒ ʒu land keͣme </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l20">vnd begert eẅch <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / ob wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> . auch ʒu Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l21"><expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd mıt <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vollreıten <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> etc . das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l22">wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> / Vnd tun <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>fürſıchtık<ex>eit</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / daʒ wır vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l23"><expan>erber<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> / von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> in der <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> von <expan>weinſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> ſache ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l24">werben . ʒu dem <expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> von <expan>weınſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd mıt <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l25"><expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> alſo vollreıten welln <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Vnd <expan>bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> eẅr <expan>weıſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> / Ob </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l26">es ſıch alſo machen wurde / daʒ Jr vns das denn ſo ʒeıtlıchſt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l27">Jr vor mugt / ʒu wıſſen tuet vnd auch wo eẅch deẅht daʒ eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_211_r1l28">vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> botſcheft <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan> bekemlıchſten ʒu ſamen kemen </ab>
<pb facs="#facs_212" id="105r"/>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r2l1">daʒ wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> darauf wıſſen ʒu <expan>fertıg<ex>en</ex></expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_212_r2l2"><expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>ıp<ex>ſ</ex>a</expan> dıe <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan> Lucye </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_211" id="104v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Des <expan>heilig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>römische<ex>n</ex></expan> reichs stette
                            <expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> der
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>eynu<ex>n</ex>ge</expan> in Swoben, umb den Bodemsee
                        und in Franken und auch der <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> stette in Swoben
                        under Ek und in Franken als sie nehst zu Ulme bey
                            <expan>einand<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> sein, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>besund<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt wie ir von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> guten frewnd der von
                                <expan>Weinsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> meynet, ewr erber
                            <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zutun zu dem edeln
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> zu <expan>Weinsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>, ob der
                        in kürcz zu land keͣme und begert ewch <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>, ob wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erb<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auch zu im <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und mit <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> vollreiten <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Und tun <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürsichtik<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                        wir unser <expan>erber<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> in der <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Weinsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> sache zu werben zu dem
                                <expan>obgen<ex>anten</ex></expan> von
                            <expan>Weinsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> und mit <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> also vollreiten welln
                                <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        ewr <expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>, ob es sich also machen wurde, daz ir
                        uns das denn so zeitlichst ir vor mugt zu wissen tuet und auch wo ewch
                        dewht, daz ewr und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erb<ex>er</ex>n</expan> botscheft <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        bekemlichsten zu samen kemen, <pb facs="#facs_212" id="105r"/>daz wir
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> darauf wissen zu
                            <expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>ip<ex>s</ex>a</expan> die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>e</expan>
                        Lucye.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
